v1.0.0 - uproot version
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
It uses uprrot both to find the baskets and to decompress them.

Requires a modification on th uprrot library, the misc.tree.py file has to be changed for the one int ehe package
directory "/lib/python2.7/site-packages/uproot/tree.py"
=======================================================================================================================


v2.0.0 - uproot to list baskets
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
It uses uproot to create the list of baskets that need to be decompressed. Then the baskets are decompressed using
the decompress() routines directly withouth the use of uproot

=======================================================================================================================


v3.0.0
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Introduces parallelism
=======================================================================================================================

v4.0.0
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Uses a DB to keep track of analyzed files
- do not create a dictionary of cinfo file, but check that a cinfo file exists when about to analyze an incomplete
    xrootd file
=======================================================================================================================

